{
  "left": "The Buddha <div><br></div><div>The Buddha, whose personal name was Siddhattha (Siddhārtha in Sanskrit), and family name Gotama (Skt. Gautama), lived in North India in the 6th century B.C. His father, Suddhodana, was the ruler of the kingdom of the Sākyas (in modern Nepal). His mother was queen Māyā. According to the custom of the time, he was married quite young, at the age of sixteen, to a beautiful and devoted young princess named Yasodharā. The young prince lived in his palace with every luxury at his command. But all of a sudden, confronted with the reality of life and the suffering of mankind, he decided to find the solution—the way out of this universal suffering. At the age of 29, soon after the birth of his only child, Rāhula, he left his kingdom and became an ascetic in search of this solution. For six years the ascetic Gotama wandered about the valley of the Ganges, meeting famous relgious teachers, studying and following their systems and methods, and submitting himself to rigorous ascetic practices. They did not satisfy him. So he abandoned all traditional religions and their methods and went his own way. It was thus that one evening, seated under a tree (since then known as the Bodhi- or Bo-tree, ‘the Tree of Wisdom’), on the bank of the river Neranjarā at Buddha-Gaya (near Gaya in modern Bihar), at the age of 3 5, Gotama attained Enlightenment, after which he was known as the Buddha, ‘The Enlightened One’. After his Enlightenment, Gotama the Buddha delivered his first sermon to a group of five ascetics, his old colleagues, in the Deer Park at Isipatana (modern Sarnath) near Benares. From that day, for 45 years, he taught all classes of men and women—kings and peasants, Brahmins and outcasts, bankers and beggars, holy men and robbers—without making the slightest distinction between them. He recognized no differences of caste or social groupings, and the Way he preached was open to all men and women who were ready to understand and to follow it. At the age of 80, the Buddha passed away at Kusinārā (in modern Uttar Pradesh in India). Today Buddhism is found in Ceylon, Burma, Thailand, Cambodia, Laos, Vietnam, Tibet, China, Japan, Mongolia, Korea, Formosa, in some parts of India, Pakistan and Nepal, and also in the Soviet Union. The Buddhist population of the world is over 500 million.\n\nRahula, Walpola. What the Buddha Taught (English Edition) (pp. 18-19). (Function). Kindle Edition. </div>",
  "right": "<div><div class=\"qMYqUG_convSearchResultHighlightRoot qMYqUG_convSearchResultTextHighlightSafari\" style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\"><div class=\"\" data-turn-id-container=\"request-WEB:05b618cc-db69-407c-a249-984a8303e575-21\" data-is-intersecting=\"true\"><section class=\"text-token-text-primary w-full focus:outline-none has-data-writing-block:pointer-events-none [&amp;:has([data-writing-block])&gt;*]:pointer-events-auto R6Vx5W_threadScrollVars scroll-mb-[calc(var(--scroll-root-safe-area-inset-bottom,0px)+var(--thread-response-height))] scroll-mt-[calc(var(--header-height)+min(200px,max(70px,20svh)))]\" dir=\"auto\" data-turn-id=\"request-WEB:05b618cc-db69-407c-a249-984a8303e575-21\" data-turn-id-container=\"request-WEB:05b618cc-db69-407c-a249-984a8303e575-21\" data-testid=\"conversation-turn-8\" data-turn=\"assistant\"><div class=\"text-base my-auto mx-auto pb-10 [--thread-content-margin:var(--thread-content-margin-xs,calc(var(--spacing)*4))] @w-sm/main:[--thread-content-margin:var(--thread-content-margin-sm,calc(var(--spacing)*6))] @w-lg/main:[--thread-content-margin:var(--thread-content-margin-lg,calc(var(--spacing)*16))] px-(--thread-content-margin)\"><div data-conversation-screenshot-content=\"\" class=\"[--thread-content-max-width:40rem] @w-lg/main:[--thread-content-max-width:48rem] mx-auto max-w-(--thread-content-max-width) flex-1 group/turn-messages focus-visible:outline-hidden relative flex w-full min-w-0 flex-col agent-turn\"><div class=\"flex max-w-full flex-col gap-4 grow\"><div data-message-author-role=\"assistant\" data-message-id=\"ba415b3b-76a6-412f-bf3b-282e9ce18a6d\" dir=\"auto\" data-message-model-slug=\"gpt-5-5\" class=\"min-h-8 text-message relative flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 text-start break-words whitespace-normal outline-none keyboard-focused:focus-ring [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-1\" data-turn-start-message=\"true\" tabindex=\"0\"><div class=\"flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden\"><div class=\"markdown prose dark:prose-invert wrap-break-word w-full light markdown-new-styling\"><h1 data-section-id=\"1q4dwc\" data-start=\"129\" data-end=\"134\" class=\"PDq2pG_selectionAnchorContainer\">第1文<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"PDq2pG_selectionAnchor\"></span></h1><blockquote data-start=\"136\" data-end=\"298\"><p data-start=\"138\" data-end=\"298\"><strong data-start=\"138\" data-end=\"298\">The Buddha, whose personal name was Siddhattha (Siddhārtha in Sanskrit), and family name Gotama (Skt. Gautama), lived in North India in the 6th century B.C.</strong></p></blockquote><hr data-start=\"300\" data-end=\"303\"><h2 data-section-id=\"1y2aktx\" data-start=\"305\" data-end=\"319\">スラッシュリーディング</h2><p data-start=\"321\" data-end=\"332\">The Buddha,</p><p data-start=\"334\" data-end=\"370\">/ whose personal name was Siddhattha</p><p data-start=\"372\" data-end=\"399\">/ (Siddhārtha in Sanskrit),</p><p data-start=\"401\" data-end=\"425\">/ and family name Gotama</p><p data-start=\"427\" data-end=\"444\">/ (Skt. Gautama),</p><p data-start=\"446\" data-end=\"453\">/ lived</p><p data-start=\"455\" data-end=\"471\">/ in North India</p><p data-start=\"473\" data-end=\"498\">/ in the 6th century B.C.</p><hr data-start=\"500\" data-end=\"503\"><h2 data-section-id=\"14wt4xg\" data-start=\"505\" data-end=\"513\">語順どおり</h2><p data-start=\"515\" data-end=\"525\">The Buddha</p><p data-start=\"527\" data-end=\"533\">→ ブッダは</p><p data-start=\"535\" data-end=\"569\">whose personal name was Siddhattha</p><p data-start=\"571\" data-end=\"587\">→ 個人名（名前）はシッダッタで</p><p data-start=\"589\" data-end=\"613\">(Siddhārtha in Sanskrit)</p><p data-start=\"615\" data-end=\"633\">→ サンスクリット語ではシッダールタ</p><p data-start=\"635\" data-end=\"657\">and family name Gotama</p><p data-start=\"659\" data-end=\"667\">→ 姓はゴータマ</p><p data-start=\"669\" data-end=\"674\">lived</p><p data-start=\"676\" data-end=\"683\">→ 生きていた</p><p data-start=\"685\" data-end=\"699\">in North India</p><p data-start=\"701\" data-end=\"708\">→ 北インドで</p><p data-start=\"710\" data-end=\"733\">in the 6th century B.C.</p><p data-start=\"735\" data-end=\"744\">→ 紀元前6世紀に</p><hr data-start=\"746\" data-end=\"749\"><h2 data-section-id=\"1dzuv8g\" data-start=\"751\" data-end=\"758\">自然な訳</h2><blockquote data-start=\"760\" data-end=\"834\"><p data-start=\"762\" data-end=\"834\"><strong data-start=\"762\" data-end=\"834\">「ブッダは、個人名をシッダッタ（サンスクリット語ではシッダールタ）、姓をゴータマといい、紀元前6世紀ごろの北インドに生きた人物である。」</strong></p></blockquote><hr data-start=\"836\" data-end=\"839\"><h3 data-section-id=\"1hsa1a8\" data-start=\"841\" data-end=\"847\">単語</h3><ul data-start=\"849\" data-end=\"929\"><li data-section-id=\"1kcsezu\" data-start=\"849\" data-end=\"869\">personal name = 名前</li><li data-section-id=\"1q94ibb\" data-start=\"870\" data-end=\"887\">family name = 姓</li><li data-section-id=\"19mph8q\" data-start=\"888\" data-end=\"901\">lived = 生きた</li><li data-section-id=\"15b1ogl\" data-start=\"902\" data-end=\"929\">B.C. = Before Christ（紀元前）</li></ul><hr data-start=\"931\" data-end=\"934\"><h1 data-section-id=\"1q4e0v\" data-start=\"936\" data-end=\"941\">第2文</h1><blockquote data-start=\"943\" data-end=\"1034\"><p data-start=\"945\" data-end=\"1034\"><strong data-start=\"945\" data-end=\"1034\">His father, Suddhodana, was the ruler of the kingdom of the Sākyas (in modern Nepal).</strong></p></blockquote><hr data-start=\"1036\" data-end=\"1039\"><h2 data-section-id=\"18oo4zo\" data-start=\"1041\" data-end=\"1049\">スラッシュ</h2><p data-start=\"1051\" data-end=\"1062\">His father,</p><p data-start=\"1064\" data-end=\"1077\">/ Suddhodana,</p><p data-start=\"1079\" data-end=\"1084\">/ was</p><p data-start=\"1086\" data-end=\"1097\">/ the ruler</p><p data-start=\"1099\" data-end=\"1129\">/ of the kingdom of the Sākyas</p><p data-start=\"1131\" data-end=\"1151\">/ (in modern Nepal).</p><hr data-start=\"1153\" data-end=\"1156\"><h2 data-section-id=\"1m16f1\" data-start=\"1158\" data-end=\"1163\">語順</h2><p data-start=\"1165\" data-end=\"1175\">His father</p><p data-start=\"1177\" data-end=\"1181\">→ 父は</p><p data-start=\"1183\" data-end=\"1193\">Suddhodana</p><p data-start=\"1195\" data-end=\"1206\">→ シュッドーダナ王で</p><p data-start=\"1208\" data-end=\"1211\">was</p><p data-start=\"1213\" data-end=\"1220\">→ ～であった</p><p data-start=\"1222\" data-end=\"1231\">the ruler</p><p data-start=\"1233\" data-end=\"1238\">→ 統治者</p><p data-start=\"1240\" data-end=\"1268\">of the kingdom of the Sākyas</p><p data-start=\"1270\" data-end=\"1281\">→ シャーキャ族の国の</p><hr data-start=\"1283\" data-end=\"1286\"><h2 data-section-id=\"1dzuv8g\" data-start=\"1288\" data-end=\"1295\">自然な訳</h2><blockquote data-start=\"1297\" data-end=\"1343\"><p data-start=\"1299\" data-end=\"1343\"><strong data-start=\"1299\" data-end=\"1343\">「父シュッドーダナは、現在のネパール付近にあったシャーキャ族の国の王であった。」</strong></p></blockquote><hr data-start=\"1345\" data-end=\"1348\"><h2 data-section-id=\"1mwskj\" data-start=\"1350\" data-end=\"1355\">単語</h2><ul data-start=\"1357\" data-end=\"1387\"><li data-section-id=\"1owrvwk\" data-start=\"1357\" data-end=\"1372\">ruler = 支配者、王</li><li data-section-id=\"swmm6m\" data-start=\"1373\" data-end=\"1387\">kingdom = 王国</li></ul><hr data-start=\"1389\" data-end=\"1392\"><h1 data-section-id=\"1q4dum\" data-start=\"1394\" data-end=\"1399\">第3文</h1><blockquote data-start=\"1401\" data-end=\"1433\"><p data-start=\"1403\" data-end=\"1433\"><strong data-start=\"1403\" data-end=\"1433\">His mother was queen Māyā.</strong></p></blockquote><p data-start=\"1435\" data-end=\"1441\">簡単ですね。</p><p data-start=\"1443\" data-end=\"1454\">母はマーヤー妃でした。</p><hr data-start=\"1456\" data-end=\"1459\"><h1 data-section-id=\"1q4drt\" data-start=\"1461\" data-end=\"1466\">第4文</h1><blockquote data-start=\"1468\" data-end=\"1512\"><p data-start=\"1470\" data-end=\"1512\"><strong data-start=\"1470\" data-end=\"1512\">According to the custom of the time...</strong></p></blockquote><hr data-start=\"1514\" data-end=\"1517\"><h2 data-section-id=\"18oo4zo\" data-start=\"1519\" data-end=\"1527\">スラッシュ</h2><p data-start=\"1529\" data-end=\"1565\">According to the custom of the time,</p><p data-start=\"1567\" data-end=\"1583\">/ he was married</p><p data-start=\"1585\" data-end=\"1599\">/ quite young,</p><p data-start=\"1601\" data-end=\"1625\">/ at the age of sixteen,</p><p data-start=\"1627\" data-end=\"1670\">/ to a beautiful and devoted young princess</p><p data-start=\"1672\" data-end=\"1690\">/ named Yasodharā.</p><hr data-start=\"1692\" data-end=\"1695\"><h2 data-section-id=\"1m16f1\" data-start=\"1697\" data-end=\"1702\">語順</h2><p data-start=\"1704\" data-end=\"1739\">According to the custom of the time</p><p data-start=\"1741\" data-end=\"1752\">→ 当時の習慣に従って</p><p data-start=\"1754\" data-end=\"1768\">he was married</p><p data-start=\"1770\" data-end=\"1778\">→ 彼は結婚した</p><p data-start=\"1780\" data-end=\"1791\">quite young</p><p data-start=\"1793\" data-end=\"1802\">→ かなり若くして</p><p data-start=\"1804\" data-end=\"1825\">at the age of sixteen</p><p data-start=\"1827\" data-end=\"1833\">→ 16歳で</p><p data-start=\"1835\" data-end=\"1876\">to a beautiful and devoted young princess</p><p data-start=\"1878\" data-end=\"1890\">→ 美しく献身的な王女と</p><p data-start=\"1892\" data-end=\"1907\">named Yasodharā</p><p data-start=\"1909\" data-end=\"1923\">→ ヤショーダラーという名の</p><hr data-start=\"1925\" data-end=\"1928\"><h2 data-section-id=\"1dzuv8g\" data-start=\"1930\" data-end=\"1937\">自然な訳</h2><blockquote data-start=\"1939\" data-end=\"1993\"><p data-start=\"1941\" data-end=\"1993\"><strong data-start=\"1941\" data-end=\"1993\">「当時の慣習に従い、彼は16歳という若さで、ヤショーダラーという美しく献身的な王女と結婚した。」</strong></p></blockquote><hr data-start=\"1995\" data-end=\"1998\"><h3 data-section-id=\"1hsa1a8\" data-start=\"2000\" data-end=\"2006\">単語</h3><ul data-start=\"2008\" data-end=\"2061\"><li data-section-id=\"kqk3xz\" data-start=\"2008\" data-end=\"2030\">according to = ～によれば</li><li data-section-id=\"zmg4pj\" data-start=\"2031\" data-end=\"2044\">custom = 習慣</li><li data-section-id=\"1djng37\" data-start=\"2045\" data-end=\"2061\">devoted = 献身的な</li></ul><hr data-start=\"2063\" data-end=\"2066\"><h1 data-section-id=\"3748p3\" data-start=\"2068\" data-end=\"2071\">次</h1><blockquote data-start=\"2073\" data-end=\"2149\"><p data-start=\"2075\" data-end=\"2149\"><strong data-start=\"2075\" data-end=\"2149\">The young prince lived in his palace with every luxury at his command.</strong></p></blockquote><hr data-start=\"2151\" data-end=\"2154\"><h2 data-section-id=\"18oo4zo\" data-start=\"2156\" data-end=\"2164\">スラッシュ</h2><p data-start=\"2166\" data-end=\"2182\">The young prince</p><p data-start=\"2184\" data-end=\"2191\">/ lived</p><p data-start=\"2193\" data-end=\"2208\">/ in his palace</p><p data-start=\"2210\" data-end=\"2229\">/ with every luxury</p><p data-start=\"2231\" data-end=\"2248\">/ at his command.</p><hr data-start=\"2250\" data-end=\"2253\"><h2 data-section-id=\"1m16f1\" data-start=\"2255\" data-end=\"2260\">語順</h2><p data-start=\"2262\" data-end=\"2278\">The young prince</p><p data-start=\"2280\" data-end=\"2287\">→ 若き王子は</p><p data-start=\"2289\" data-end=\"2294\">lived</p><p data-start=\"2296\" data-end=\"2304\">→ 暮らしていた</p><p data-start=\"2306\" data-end=\"2319\">in his palace</p><p data-start=\"2321\" data-end=\"2326\">→ 宮殿で</p><p data-start=\"2328\" data-end=\"2345\">with every luxury</p><p data-start=\"2347\" data-end=\"2358\">→ あらゆる贅沢を備え</p><p data-start=\"2360\" data-end=\"2374\">at his command</p><p data-start=\"2376\" data-end=\"2384\">→ 思いのままに</p><hr data-start=\"2386\" data-end=\"2389\"><h2 data-section-id=\"1dzuv8g\" data-start=\"2391\" data-end=\"2398\">自然な訳</h2><blockquote data-start=\"2400\" data-end=\"2440\"><p data-start=\"2402\" data-end=\"2440\"><strong data-start=\"2402\" data-end=\"2440\">「若き王子は、望むものは何でも手に入る贅沢な宮殿生活を送っていた。」</strong></p></blockquote><hr data-start=\"2442\" data-end=\"2445\"><h3 data-section-id=\"1hsffzb\" data-start=\"2447\" data-end=\"2453\">熟語</h3><p data-start=\"2455\" data-end=\"2475\"><strong data-start=\"2455\" data-end=\"2475\">at one's command</strong></p><p data-start=\"2477\" data-end=\"2486\">思いのままに使える</p><p data-start=\"2488\" data-end=\"2493\">自由になる</p><hr data-start=\"2495\" data-end=\"2498\"><h1 data-section-id=\"89l91g\" data-start=\"2500\" data-end=\"2511\">ここから有名な部分</h1><blockquote data-start=\"2513\" data-end=\"2541\"><p data-start=\"2515\" data-end=\"2541\"><strong data-start=\"2515\" data-end=\"2541\">But all of a sudden...</strong></p></blockquote><hr data-start=\"2543\" data-end=\"2546\"><h2 data-section-id=\"18oo4zo\" data-start=\"2548\" data-end=\"2556\">スラッシュ</h2><p data-start=\"2558\" data-end=\"2561\">But</p><p data-start=\"2563\" data-end=\"2581\">/ all of a sudden,</p><p data-start=\"2583\" data-end=\"2600\">/ confronted with</p><p data-start=\"2602\" data-end=\"2623\">/ the reality of life</p><p data-start=\"2625\" data-end=\"2656\">/ and the suffering of mankind,</p><p data-start=\"2658\" data-end=\"2670\">/ he decided</p><p data-start=\"2672\" data-end=\"2681\">/ to find</p><p data-start=\"2683\" data-end=\"2698\">/ the solution—</p><p data-start=\"2700\" data-end=\"2713\">/ the way out</p><p data-start=\"2715\" data-end=\"2745\">/ of this universal suffering.</p><hr data-start=\"2747\" data-end=\"2750\"><h2 data-section-id=\"1m16f1\" data-start=\"2752\" data-end=\"2757\">語順</h2><p data-start=\"2759\" data-end=\"2762\">しかし</p><p data-start=\"2764\" data-end=\"2766\">突然</p><p data-start=\"2768\" data-end=\"2774\">人生の現実と</p><p data-start=\"2776\" data-end=\"2783\">人類の苦しみに</p><p data-start=\"2785\" data-end=\"2788\">直面し</p><p data-start=\"2790\" data-end=\"2796\">彼は決意した</p><p data-start=\"2798\" data-end=\"2804\">見つけようと</p><p data-start=\"2806\" data-end=\"2812\">その解決法を</p><p data-start=\"2814\" data-end=\"2817\">つまり</p><p data-start=\"2819\" data-end=\"2833\">この普遍的苦しみからの出口を</p><hr data-start=\"2835\" data-end=\"2838\"><h2 data-section-id=\"1dzuv8g\" data-start=\"2840\" data-end=\"2847\">自然な訳</h2><blockquote data-start=\"2849\" data-end=\"2914\"><p data-start=\"2851\" data-end=\"2914\"><strong data-start=\"2851\" data-end=\"2914\">「しかしある日突然、人生の現実と人々の苦しみに直面した彼は、その普遍的な苦しみから抜け出す道を見つけようと決意した。」</strong></p></blockquote><hr data-start=\"2916\" data-end=\"2919\"><h3 data-section-id=\"1hsa1a8\" data-start=\"2921\" data-end=\"2927\">単語</h3><ul data-start=\"2929\" data-end=\"3020\"><li data-section-id=\"shuvdw\" data-start=\"2929\" data-end=\"2955\">confronted with = ～に直面する</li><li data-section-id=\"1482kcq\" data-start=\"2956\" data-end=\"2970\">reality = 現実</li><li data-section-id=\"14cpdyi\" data-start=\"2971\" data-end=\"2988\">suffering = 苦しみ</li><li data-section-id=\"z4yeet\" data-start=\"2989\" data-end=\"3004\">solution = 解決</li><li data-section-id=\"1av5j30\" data-start=\"3005\" data-end=\"3020\">way out = 脱出口</li></ul><hr data-start=\"3022\" data-end=\"3025\"><h2 data-section-id=\"6a4brq\" data-start=\"3027\" data-end=\"3034\">内容解説</h2><p data-start=\"3036\" data-end=\"3075\">ここでいう「人生の現実」とは、仏教で有名な「四門出遊」の物語です。王宮の外で、</p><ul data-start=\"3077\" data-end=\"3097\"><li data-section-id=\"yiadtf\" data-start=\"3077\" data-end=\"3081\">老人</li><li data-section-id=\"yhqh87\" data-start=\"3082\" data-end=\"3086\">病人</li><li data-section-id=\"yhrbcm\" data-start=\"3087\" data-end=\"3091\">死者</li><li data-section-id=\"1wtaj3\" data-start=\"3092\" data-end=\"3097\">修行者</li></ul><p data-start=\"3099\" data-end=\"3144\">に出会い、「人は老い・病み・死ぬ」という避けられない現実に衝撃を受けたと伝えられています。</p><hr data-start=\"3146\" data-end=\"3149\"><h1 data-section-id=\"yhu3fu\" data-start=\"3151\" data-end=\"3155\">出家</h1><blockquote data-start=\"3157\" data-end=\"3182\"><p data-start=\"3159\" data-end=\"3182\"><strong data-start=\"3159\" data-end=\"3182\">At the age of 29...</strong></p></blockquote><p data-start=\"3184\" data-end=\"3188\">29歳で</p><p data-start=\"3190\" data-end=\"3204\">唯一の息子ラーフラ誕生直後に</p><p data-start=\"3206\" data-end=\"3211\">王宮を去り</p><p data-start=\"3213\" data-end=\"3222\">修行者になります。</p><hr data-start=\"3224\" data-end=\"3227\"><h2 data-section-id=\"1mwskj\" data-start=\"3229\" data-end=\"3234\">単語</h2><ul data-start=\"3236\" data-end=\"3255\"><li data-section-id=\"19zbm9i\" data-start=\"3236\" data-end=\"3255\">ascetic = 修行者、苦行者</li></ul><hr data-start=\"3257\" data-end=\"3260\"><h1 data-section-id=\"1mxxmf\" data-start=\"3262\" data-end=\"3267\">6年間</h1><blockquote data-start=\"3269\" data-end=\"3291\"><p data-start=\"3271\" data-end=\"3291\"><strong data-start=\"3271\" data-end=\"3291\">For six years...</strong></p></blockquote><p data-start=\"3293\" data-end=\"3297\">6年間、</p><p data-start=\"3299\" data-end=\"3311\">さまざまな宗教家を訪ね、</p><p data-start=\"3313\" data-end=\"3319\">教えを学び、</p><p data-start=\"3321\" data-end=\"3330\">苦行も実践します。</p><p data-start=\"3332\" data-end=\"3336\">しかし、</p><blockquote data-start=\"3338\" data-end=\"3369\"><p data-start=\"3340\" data-end=\"3369\"><strong data-start=\"3340\" data-end=\"3369\">They did not satisfy him.</strong></p></blockquote><p data-start=\"3371\" data-end=\"3386\">それでは満足できませんでした。</p><hr data-start=\"3388\" data-end=\"3391\"><h2 data-section-id=\"1vfofs6\" data-start=\"3393\" data-end=\"3403\">satisfy</h2><p data-start=\"3405\" data-end=\"3410\">満足させる</p><p data-start=\"3412\" data-end=\"3417\">納得させる</p><hr data-start=\"3419\" data-end=\"3422\"><h2 data-section-id=\"1txxlac\" data-start=\"3424\" data-end=\"3432\">重要な一文</h2><blockquote data-start=\"3434\" data-end=\"3521\"><p data-start=\"3436\" data-end=\"3521\"><strong data-start=\"3436\" data-end=\"3521\">So he abandoned all traditional religions and their methods and went his own way.</strong></p></blockquote><hr data-start=\"3523\" data-end=\"3526\"><h3 data-section-id=\"b3jzlz\" data-start=\"3528\" data-end=\"3537\">スラッシュ</h3><p data-start=\"3539\" data-end=\"3541\">So</p><p data-start=\"3543\" data-end=\"3557\">/ he abandoned</p><p data-start=\"3559\" data-end=\"3586\">/ all traditional religions</p><p data-start=\"3588\" data-end=\"3607\">/ and their methods</p><p data-start=\"3609\" data-end=\"3619\">/ and went</p><p data-start=\"3621\" data-end=\"3635\">/ his own way.</p><hr data-start=\"3637\" data-end=\"3640\"><h3 data-section-id=\"fcwmrn\" data-start=\"3642\" data-end=\"3650\">自然な訳</h3><blockquote data-start=\"3652\" data-end=\"3693\"><p data-start=\"3654\" data-end=\"3693\"><strong data-start=\"3654\" data-end=\"3693\">「そこで彼は、既存の宗教や修行法をすべて離れ、自らの道を歩み始めた。」</strong></p></blockquote><hr data-start=\"3695\" data-end=\"3698\"><p data-start=\"3700\" data-end=\"3721\">ここはラーフラが特に強調している部分です。</p><p data-start=\"3723\" data-end=\"3728\">ブッダは、</p><p data-start=\"3730\" data-end=\"3740\">「既存宗教の改革者」</p><p data-start=\"3742\" data-end=\"3747\">というより</p><p data-start=\"3749\" data-end=\"3782\"><strong data-start=\"3749\" data-end=\"3771\">自ら検証し、自ら道を切り開いた探究者</strong>として描かれています。</p><hr data-start=\"3784\" data-end=\"3787\"><h1 data-section-id=\"yhrec3\" data-start=\"3789\" data-end=\"3793\">悟り</h1><p data-start=\"3795\" data-end=\"3798\">35歳</p><p data-start=\"3800\" data-end=\"3811\">菩提樹の下で悟りを開き</p><p data-start=\"3813\" data-end=\"3827\"><strong data-start=\"3813\" data-end=\"3827\">The Buddha</strong></p><p data-start=\"3829\" data-end=\"3836\">「目覚めた人」</p><p data-start=\"3838\" data-end=\"3851\">と呼ばれるようになります。</p><hr data-start=\"3853\" data-end=\"3856\"><h1 data-section-id=\"h3tnl7\" data-start=\"3858\" data-end=\"3866\">初めての説法</h1><p data-start=\"3868\" data-end=\"3880\">鹿野苑（サールナート）で</p><p data-start=\"3882\" data-end=\"3899\">5人の元修行仲間に教えを説きます。</p><p data-start=\"3901\" data-end=\"3913\">これが「初転法輪」です。</p><hr data-start=\"3915\" data-end=\"3918\"><h1 data-section-id=\"1hrefwg\" data-start=\"3920\" data-end=\"3926\">45年間</h1><p data-start=\"3928\" data-end=\"3942\">ラーフラが特に強調するのは、</p><p data-start=\"3944\" data-end=\"3948\">ブッダは</p><ul data-start=\"3950\" data-end=\"3991\"><li data-section-id=\"3745k3\" data-start=\"3950\" data-end=\"3953\">王</li><li data-section-id=\"yi8saz\" data-start=\"3954\" data-end=\"3958\">農民</li><li data-section-id=\"1bisxfk\" data-start=\"3959\" data-end=\"3965\">バラモン</li><li data-section-id=\"yi9eql\" data-start=\"3966\" data-end=\"3970\">賤民</li><li data-section-id=\"25kvgy\" data-start=\"3971\" data-end=\"3976\">銀行家</li><li data-section-id=\"yhxzs9\" data-start=\"3977\" data-end=\"3981\">乞食</li><li data-section-id=\"yiapx7\" data-start=\"3982\" data-end=\"3986\">聖者</li><li data-section-id=\"yhp8r9\" data-start=\"3987\" data-end=\"3991\">盗賊</li></ul><p data-start=\"3993\" data-end=\"4013\">すべてに同じように教えを説いたことです。</p><blockquote data-start=\"4015\" data-end=\"4079\"><p data-start=\"4017\" data-end=\"4079\"><strong data-start=\"4017\" data-end=\"4079\">He recognized no differences of caste or social groupings.</strong></p></blockquote><p data-start=\"4081\" data-end=\"4106\">「カーストや社会的身分による違いを認めなかった。」</p><p data-start=\"4108\" data-end=\"4134\">これは当時のインド社会では非常に革新的な姿勢でした。</p><hr data-start=\"4136\" data-end=\"4139\"><h1 data-section-id=\"yhtwti\" data-start=\"4141\" data-end=\"4145\">入滅</h1><p data-start=\"4147\" data-end=\"4158\">80歳で亡くなります。</p><p data-start=\"4160\" data-end=\"4164\">英語では</p><blockquote data-start=\"4166\" data-end=\"4183\"><p data-start=\"4168\" data-end=\"4183\"><strong data-start=\"4168\" data-end=\"4183\">passed away</strong></p></blockquote><p data-start=\"4185\" data-end=\"4203\">という穏やかな表現が使われています。</p><hr data-start=\"4205\" data-end=\"4208\"><h1 data-section-id=\"464005\" data-start=\"4210\" data-end=\"4219\">今日のポイント</h1><p data-start=\"4221\" data-end=\"4279\">この章は単なる伝記ではありません。ラーフラは、ブッダを「神秘的な存在」としてではなく、一人の人間として描いています。</p><p data-start=\"4281\" data-end=\"4292\">流れは非常に明確です。</p><ol data-start=\"4294\" data-end=\"4387\"><li data-section-id=\"ywldj0\" data-start=\"4294\" data-end=\"4307\">王子として生まれる。</li><li data-section-id=\"1sdkbq\" data-start=\"4308\" data-end=\"4321\">苦しみの現実を知る。</li><li data-section-id=\"5scyj7\" data-start=\"4322\" data-end=\"4339\">あらゆる宗教・修行法を試す。</li><li data-section-id=\"gq2fln\" data-start=\"4340\" data-end=\"4357\">納得できず、自分で探究する。</li><li data-section-id=\"17pfibr\" data-start=\"4358\" data-end=\"4367\">悟りを得る。</li><li data-section-id=\"1jr0jyl\" data-start=\"4368\" data-end=\"4387\">身分を問わず45年間教え続ける。</li></ol><p data-start=\"4389\" data-end=\"4443\">この構成を見ると、ラーフラはブッダを**「真理を自ら探究した実践者」**として紹介していることが分かります。</p><hr data-start=\"4445\" data-end=\"4448\"><h3 data-section-id=\"178fxmw\" data-start=\"4450\" data-end=\"4461\">あなたへの補足</h3><p data-start=\"4463\" data-end=\"4574\">あなたは以前、「<strong data-start=\"4471\" data-end=\"4480\">時間＝生命</strong>」や「<strong data-start=\"4483\" data-end=\"4488\">縁</strong>」を軸に仏教を読み直したいと話していました。その視点から見ると、この章ではまだ哲学そのものではなく、「ブッダという人物が、なぜ探究を始めたのか」という動機が描かれています。</p><p data-start=\"4576\" data-end=\"4684\" data-is-last-node=\"\" data-is-only-node=\"\">つまり、ブッダの出発点は「世界の仕組みを説明したい」という知的好奇心ではなく、<strong data-start=\"4615\" data-end=\"4647\">「苦しみをどうすれば終わらせられるのか」という切実な問い</strong>でした。この問題意識が、この後に続く四諦や縁起の教え全体の土台になります。</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"z-0 flex min-h-[46px] justify-start\"></div><div class=\"mt-3 w-full empty:hidden\"><div class=\"text-center\"></div></div></div></div></section></div></div></div><div></div><div><div></div></div>",
  "sync": true
}
